{"word":"Offerings","slug":"offerings","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Offerings</b> Offered at the door:<br/> - Of the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=1&verse=3'>Lev 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=3&verse=2'>Lev 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=4'>Lev 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=9'>Lev 17:9</a> <br/> - Of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=12'>2Ch 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=62'>1Ki 8:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=27'>1Ki 12:27</a> <br/> All animal sacrifices must be eight days old or over<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=27'>Lev 22:27</a><br/> Must be:<br/> - Salted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=13'>Lev 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=43&verse=24'>Eze 43:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=49'>Mar 9:49</a> <br/> - Accompanied with leaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=13'>Lev 7:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=5'>Amo 4:5</a> <br/> - Without leaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=18'>Exo 23:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=25'>Exo 34:25</a> <br/> Eaten<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=13'>1Sa 9:13</a><br/> Ordinance relating to scapegoat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=26'>Lev 16:26</a><br/><a href='S:Atonement'>Atonement</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=51&verse=17'>Psa 51:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wo